        <Parent_String>hatters [300025354], textile workers by product [300168309], textile workers [300025349], people in crafts and trades by material [300025281], people in crafts and trades [300025253], people by occupation [300024980], people (agents) [300024979], People (hierarchy name) [300024978], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
